sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Cust as 顧客
  participant Web as Web フロント
  participant API as FastAPI
  participant Claude as Claude API
  participant DB as PostgreSQL

  Cust->>Web: 注文を入力
  Web->>API: POST /orders (JSON)
  API->>DB: INSERT orders
  API->>Claude: 「住所を整形して」
  Claude-->>API: 整形済み住所
  API->>DB: UPDATE orders SET address=...
  API-->>Web: 200 OK + 受注番号
  Web-->>Cust: 完了画面
